---
title: Middle Eastern-Style Chickpea & Veggie Bowl with Garlic Dip & Tortilla Chips
description: When you simmer hearty chickpeas with subtly sweet veggies, garlicky tomatoes and our chermoula spice blend, the result is
pretty magical. Serve with a garlic dip for creaminess and of course oven baked tortilla chips for crunch, and scooping!
